            <div xml:id="Aink307">
            <lg type="edition">
            <l>ñelikaḻai muḻaṅkaḻal vayamā verūuṅ</l>
            <l>kuṉṟuṭai yaruñcurañ celavayarn taṉaiyē</l>
            <l>naṉṟil koṇkaniṉ poruḷē</l>
            <l>pāvai yaṉṉaniṉ ṟuṇaippirintu varumē</l>                                        </l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
              <l>You made up your mind to go to the harsh wasteland full of hills,</l>
              <l>Where roaring fire [that sparked from] rubbing bamboos frightens tiger!</l>
              <l>Seashore-dweller! You wealth isn’t worth</l>
              <l>separating from your doll-like girl.</l>
              </lg>
        </div>
